    <h1>Privacy Policy for Ads Impression Calculator</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 21, 2025</p>
    
    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>Ads Impression Calculator does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. All calculations are performed locally on your device.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Calculation history is stored locally on your device using browser localStorage and is never transmitted to external servers. Your data remains private and under your control.</p>
    
    <h2>Network Access</h2>
    <p>This application does not access the internet and works completely offline. No data is sent to or received from any external servers.</p>
    
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This app does not use any third-party analytics, tracking services, or advertising networks.</p>
    
    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This app does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13 years of age.</p>
    
